Package: squelch
Version: 1.0.1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: fail2ban, iptables, openssh-server, curl, wget
Maintainer: Squelch Security <security@squelch.dev>
Description: Comprehensive server security and monitoring suite
 Squelch provides a complete security hardening solution for Debian servers,
 including:
 .
  * fail2ban configuration with custom filters for HTTP/SSH attacks
  * SSH hardening with key-based authentication and port changes
  * Security monitoring tools and dashboards
  * Automated attack detection and IP blocking
  * Real-time security status reporting
 .
 This package configures a production-ready security setup suitable for
 web servers, reverse proxies, and general-purpose Linux servers.
